QuestData.Title: Trophy of Glory: Fungal Praetorian
QuestData.Description: Defeating the Fungal Praetorian has yielded you a trophy worthy of acclaim.$b$bTake this to Maraad at Highpass.
QuestData.LogDescription: Take the trophy to Maraad at Highpass in Gorgrond.
QuestData.RewardText: I've heard tales of the Crimson Fen from the rangari; no one has yet returned from there. If this was the reason then we can all breathe safer now.
